    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made this over the weekend using Hendricks gin &#8211; I&#8217;m sure it was delicious with Tanqueray, but with Hendricks, believe me, it&#8217;s divine. It&#8217;s more of an herby gin, with a slight bit of citrus. It&#8217;s known as the gin you should garnish with cucumber, instead of lime.</p>
    </div>

